401}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 25769, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2956, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 366776, "username": "Davic1", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Davic1", "website": "posts.luozx.org", "twitter": "luozxdotorg", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6ac3c6a1a3f8f68f2eac068a8943d7cb?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6ac3c6a1a3f8f68f2eac068a8943d7cb?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6ac3c6a1a3f8f68f2eac068a8943d7cb?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1543538317, "last_modified": 1711974387}, "last_reply_by": "jtskyin", "last_touched": 1718316747, "title": "航旅纵横的替代品有推荐的吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1049292", "created": 1718267918, "deleted": 0, "content": "航旅纵横 全是广告和购物，太傻逼了。\r\n\r\n目前看到了两款 App：\r\n\r\n1. App in the Air\r\n\t- 比较喜欢里面的常旅客计划，能添加很多会员，一起管理\r\n    - 首页的航班预订，国内好像都用不了（从香港出发到国内的能搜出来，其他国内飞国内，都搜不出来）\r\n\r\n2. Flightly\r\n\t- 功能专一\r\n    - 订阅价格比 App in the Air 贵\r\n    \r\n有 V 友用过这两款或者其他 App 吗？ 有没有推荐的", "content_rendered": "<p>航旅纵横 全是广告和购物，太傻逼了。</p>\n<p>目前看到了两款 App：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>App in the Air</p>\n<ul>\n<li>比较喜欢里面的常旅客计划，能添加很多会员，一起管理</li>\n<li>首页的航班预订，国内好像都用不了（从香港出发到国内的能搜出来，其他国内飞国内，都搜不出来）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Flightly</p>\n<ul>\n<li>功能专一</li>\n<li>订阅价格比 App in the Air 贵</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>有 V 友用过这两款或者其他 App 吗？ 有没有推荐的</p>\n", "last_modified": 1718267918, "replies": 60, "id": 1049292}]